List of templates in the KEGG REST API

Source: R/keggrest.R
kegg_api_templates.Rd

List of templates in the KEGG REST API

Usage

kegg_api_templates()

Value

A list of KEGG API templates.

Examples

kegg_api_templates()
#> $info
#> $info[[1]]
#> $info[[1]]$database
#>  [1] "pathway"  "brite"    "module"   "ko"       "genome"   "vg"
